<title>USA: FTC wants more information on Cadence merger.</title>
<headline>FTC wants more information on Cadence merger.</headline>
<dateline>SAN JOSE, Calif. 1997-01-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Cadence Design Systems Inc said the U.S. Federal Trade Commission has requested additional information from the company and from Cooper &amp; Chyan Technology Inc relating to their proposed merger.</p>
<p>Cadence said the companies plan to respond promptly to the FTC request.</p>
<p>Cooper &amp; Chyan stockholders are scheduled to meet on Jan. 24 to vote on the stock swap agreement, Cadence said.</p>
